ğŸ”¹ CRUD APIs
1. /api/master-years
   -> GET, POST, DELETE

2. /api/semesters
   -> CRUD + filter by master year

3. /api/faculties
   -> CRUD

4. /api/subjects
   -> CRUD + filter by semester

5. /api/students
   -> CRUD + filter by faculty/semester/master year

